{"ast":null,"code":"import Calendar from './Calendar2.vue';\nexport default {\n  name: 'DraWers',\n  components: {\n    Calendar\n  },\n  props: {\n    showLiveDrawer: {\n      type: Boolean,\n      default: false\n    },\n    showDrawer: {\n      type: Boolean,\n      default: false\n    },\n    showLectureDrawer: {\n      type: Boolean,\n      default: false\n    },\n    currentEventImage: {\n      type: String,\n      default: ''\n    }\n  },\n  emits: ['close-drawer', 'event-type-changed'],\n  data() {\n    return {\n      showContentA: true,\n      showContentB: false\n    };\n  },\n  methods: {\n    toggleContent() {\n      this.showContentA = true;\n      this.showContentB = false;\n    },\n    toggleContent2() {\n      this.showContentB = true;\n      this.showContentA = false;\n    },\n    handleEventTypeChange(eventType) {\n      this.$emit('event-type-changed', eventType);\n    }\n  }\n};","map":{"version":3,"names":["Calendar","name","components","props","showLiveDrawer","type","Boolean","default","showDrawer","showLectureDrawer","currentEventImage","String","emits","data","showContentA","showContentB","methods","toggleContent","toggleContent2","handleEventTypeChange","eventType","$emit"],"sources":["/Users/linhankuan/fvl2025/src/components/Drawers.vue"],"sourcesContent":["<template>\n  <!-- LiveDrawer 結構 -->\n  <div class=\"live-drawer\" :class=\"{ open: showLiveDrawer }\">\n    <button class=\"drawer-close\" @click=\"$emit('close-drawer', 'about')\">×</button>\n    <div class=\"drawer-content\">\n      <img :src=\"currentEventImage\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;z-index:999;object-fit:cover;\">\n      <div class=\"drawer-title\">\n        <h2 style=\"margin: 0;padding:10px;\">2025精選</h2>\n        <p style=\"padding:10px;\">分享C-LAB未來視覺實驗室自2020年起持續推動實驗展演計畫「FUTURE VISION LAB」，以數位實驗建築著手打造穹形場域（DOME），以探索科技媒體的視覺極限為目標，過去四年已進行百餘件作品展演。此計畫在2023年完成軟硬體升級，尺寸突破過往尺度，打造直徑15公尺、全臺唯一巨型移動式戶外沉浸式體驗空間「C-LAB穹頂劇場」。影音軟硬體歷經數次迭代開發，克服球形曲面投影的校正、融接、對位、播放控制與影像前製等多重技術之複雜度，沉浸影像投影系統總運算可達8K*8K超高解析度；內部以雙層結構隱藏影音設備，客製新型態透聲投影膜片，並與臺灣聲響實驗室攜手合作建構更完善的25.4聲道環繞聲場環境。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Drawer 結構 -->\n  <div class=\"drawer\" :class=\"{ open: showDrawer }\">\n    <button class=\"drawer-close\" @click=\"$emit('close-drawer', 'schedule')\">×</button>\n    <div class=\"drawer-content2\">\n      <div class=\"cal-page\">\n        <div class=\"cal-title\">\n          <h2 style=\"padding: 20px;color: #fff;\">FUTURE VISION LAB <br>2025 節目表</h2>\n          <Calendar @event-type-changed=\"handleEventTypeChange\" />\n        </div>\n        <img :src=\"currentEventImage\" alt=\"event image\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- 講座 Drawer 結構 -->\n  <div class=\"lecture-drawer\" :class=\"{ open: showLectureDrawer }\">\n    <button class=\"drawer-close\" @click=\"$emit('close-drawer', 'lecture')\">×</button>\n    <div class=\"logo-contain\" style=\"width: 100vw;height: auto;display:flex;justify-content: center;\">\n      <img src=\"../assets/fvl_logo.png\" style=\"width:120px;position: absolute;z-index: 999;left: 0;top:5%;\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"drawer-content\" style=\"background-color:black;color:white;\">\n      <video autoplay muted loop src=\"../assets/dome.mp4\" style=\"position: absolute;z-index: 1;right:0%;width:100%;height:70%;top:-5%; float: left;clip-path: ellipse(50% 50% at right);opacity: 0.5;object-fit:cover;\"></video>\n      <div class=\"all-content\" style=\"position: absolute;z-index: 999;height: 100%;width: 100%; flex-direction: column;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items:flex-start;\">\n        <h2 style=\"color:gainsboro;border-bottom: 2px solid white;padding: 20px;\">觀眾入場須知</h2>\n        <div class=\"list-text\" style=\"padding: 20px;\">\n          <button class=\"list-btn1\" @click=\"toggleContent()\">關於入場規章</button>\n          <button class=\"list-btn2\" @click=\"toggleContent2()\">攝錄影需知</button>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"content-container\">\n          <div class=\"lecture-list\" v-if=\"showContentA\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n            <p>參展廠商、參觀者或展館區域內人員，有下列情形且經主辦單位勸導未改善者，主辦單位得拒絕其進場或要求違反者離場，並禁止再行進入展場，不予退費：</p>\n            <p> 1.違反公共秩序或善良風俗，或影響展場形象、衛生安全，或其他影響展覽秩序之行為，包含但不限於下列之行為：</p>\n            <p>(1)騷擾、大聲咆哮、辱罵、恐嚇或傷害展場工作人員、其他相關人員。</p>\n            <p>(2)於展場使用不適當移動工具，如兩輪平衡車、滑板等。</p>\n            <p>(3)於展場酒醉失態。</p>\n            <p>(4)攜帶違禁物、爆裂物、危險物品、其物品有致人、財物等損害之虞或可能影響展場秩序、安全之物品。</p>\n            <p>(5)穿著惡臭衣服、拖鞋、攜帶不潔物品等影響展場形象。</p>\n            <p>(6)其他影響展覽進行之行為。</p>\n            <p>2.於展館從事之抗議、陳情等活動，影響展場秩序及觀展品質。</p>\n            <p>3.參展商或其他出入展場之人員拒絕依主辦單位規定之方式入場。</p>\n            <p>4.出入展場相關人員使用他人身分證明文件或變造、偽造身分證明文件。</p>\n            <p>5.展覽期間5月20至5月23日，禁止18歲以下者入場，以維持展場秩序及安全</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lecture-list\" v-if=\"showContentB\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n            <p>1.館內不開放商業攝影（例：婚紗、商品型錄、攝影教學等）或其他影響場館安全及參觀品質之拍攝。</p>\n            <p>2.館內除另有特別告示，開放非商業性攝影。為維護及尊重創作者智慧財產權， 請勿翻攝展場內錄像作品及影片。</p>\n            <p>3.攝影請勿使用閃光燈、三腳架、手持穩定器或自拍棒等各式專業器材或輔助設備。</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script>\nimport Calendar from './Calendar2.vue';\n\nexport default {\n  name: 'DraWers',\n  components: {\n    Calendar\n  },\n  props: {\n    showLiveDrawer: {\n      type: Boolean,\n      default: false\n    },\n    showDrawer: {\n      type: Boolean,\n      default: false\n    },\n    showLectureDrawer: {\n      type: Boolean,\n      default: false\n    },\n    currentEventImage: {\n      type: String,\n      default: ''\n    },\n  },\n  emits: ['close-drawer', 'event-type-changed'],\n  data() {\n    return {\n      showContentA: true,\n      showContentB: false\n    }\n  },\n  methods: {\n    toggleContent() {\n      this.showContentA = true;\n      this.showContentB = false;\n    },\n    toggleContent2() {\n      this.showContentB = true;\n      this.showContentA = false;\n    },\n    handleEventTypeChange(eventType) {\n      this.$emit('event-type-changed', eventType);\n    }\n  }\n}\n</script>\n\n<style lang=\"scss\" scoped>\n.drawer {\n  position: fixed;\n  top: 0;\n  left: 0;\n  width: 100vw;\n  max-width: 100vw;\n  height: 100vh;\n  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);\n  box-shadow: -4px 0 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);\n  z-index: 1000;\n  transform: translateX(-100%);\n  transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(.77,0,.18,1);\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  padding: 0;\n}\n\n.drawer.open {\n  transform: translateX(0);\n}\n\n.live-drawer {\n  position: fixed;\n  top: 0;\n  right: 0;\n  width: 100vw;\n  max-width: 100vw;\n  height: 100vh;\n  background: #10ffdb;\n  box-shadow: -4px 0 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);\n  z-index: 1000;\n  transform: translateX(100%);\n  transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(.77,0,.18,1);\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  padding: 0;\n}\n\n.live-drawer.open {\n  transform: translateX(0);\n}\n\n.lecture-drawer {\n  position: fixed;\n  top: 0;\n  left: 0;\n  width: 100vw;\n  height: 100vh;\n  background-color: #595959;\n  color: black;\n  z-index: 1000;\n  transform: scale(0);\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  transform-origin: bottom left;\n  transition: all 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  padding: 0;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.lecture-drawer.open {\n  transform: scale(1);\n  border-radius: 0;\n}\n\n.drawer-close {\n  align-self: flex-end;\n  font-size: 2.2rem;\n  background: none;\n  border: none;\n  color: #333;\n  margin: 18px 24px 0 0;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  z-index: 1;\n}\n\n.drawer-content {\n  position: absolute;\n  z-index: 0;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: center;\n  align-items: flex-start;\n  width: 100vw;\n  height: 100vh;\n  color: #222;\n  flex: 1;\n  overflow-y: auto;\n}\n\n.drawer-content2 {\n  width: 100vw;\n  height: 100vh;\n  color: #222;\n  padding: 0px;\n  flex: 1;\n  overflow-y: auto;\n  margin-bottom: 2em;\n}\n\n.drawer-content2 img {\n  width: 45%;\n  height: 100%;\n  padding: 0px;\n  position: fixed;\n  right: 0;\n  top: 0;\n  z-index: 0;\n  object-fit: cover;\n  display: flex;\n}\n\n.cal-page {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  flex-wrap: nowrap;\n}\n\n.cal-title {\n  width: 50%;\n  height: 100vh;\n  padding: 30px;\n}\n\n.drawer-title {\n  position: absolute;\n  width: 50%;\n  height: 50%;\n  z-index: 999;\n  color: #ffff;\n  top: 20%;\n  bottom: 50%;\n  left: 5%;\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  text-decoration: none;\n  font-family: Impact, Haettenschweiler, 'Arial Narrow Bold', sans-serif;\n  letter-spacing: 0.2rem;\n  backdrop-filter: blur(5px);\n  padding: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.lecture-drawer .drawer-content {\n  // padding: 40px 32px 32px 32px;\n  flex: 1;\n  overflow-y: auto;\n  color: white;\n}\n\n.list-text {\n  background-color: transparent;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: row;\n  gap: 10px;\n}\n\n.list-btn1 {\n  background-color: grey;\n  padding: 5px 8px;\n  border: 1px black solid;\n  color: white;\n}\n\n.list-btn2 {\n  background-color: white;\n  padding: 5px 8px;\n  border: 1px black solid;\n  color: black;\n}\n\n.list-btn2:hover {\n  background-color: #343434;\n  color: white;\n}\n\n.content-container {\n  height: 50%;\n  width: 100%;\n  min-height: 200px;\n  margin-top: 10px;\n  margin-bottom: 3em;\n}\n\n.lecture-list {\n  width: 90%;\n  margin-top: 40px;\n  padding: 20px;\n  gap: 20px;\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n\n  .drawer-content2 img {\n    display: none;\n    width: 80%;\n    height: 50%;\n    padding: 20px;\n  }\n  \n  .cal-title {\n    padding: 0;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .live-drawer {\n    max-width: 100vw;\n    width: 100vw;\n    padding: 0;\n  }\n  \n  .drawer-title {\n    width: 100%;\n    left: 0;\n  }\n  \n  .drawer-close {\n    margin: 12px 12px 0 0;\n    font-size: 2rem;\n  }\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 900px) {\n  .drawer-content2 img {\n    display: none;\n    width: 80%;\n    height: 50%;\n    padding: 20px;\n  }\n  \n  .cal-title {\n    padding: 0;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n}\n</style> "